{
  "stem": "1929.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 599.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We had to wear a yellow star and a white arm band with a-- with a Star of David saying we were Jewish.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We could not-- we could not leave the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "At first, we were able to leave outside the ghetto, and then it was restricted where we couldn't, or certain hours.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But the ghetto, the ghetto in Piotrkow was the first ghetto established by the Germans in Poland.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But it was not a fenced in ghetto like later on Warsaw was.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "It was just a restricted area section of town where Jews could live.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And even within that section of town, there were Poles and some Germans that lived there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Well, not Deutsche, volks Deutsche, Germans of-- or Poles that were of German origin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "It was kind of strange, but I remember they lived in the same houses we did.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And obviously, there was no school anymore.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "All--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We were living in a house with the one room, like one room, one and a half room.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I think at that point there is-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] I think at that point, I think my sister is there with me.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And my mother.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, my mother had returned.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She had gone to-- she had gone to Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know how.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I just don't understand the whole thing to this day, how she could have just--",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, with my sister, but she went by herself I think.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She just took off.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I don't know how, why.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Who knows?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, there was so much going on at the time.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And-- but as a kid, I don't feel myself being too affected.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I'm still wandering around the town.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 78,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "You know, I remember me and another guy go through town picking up cigarette butts.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
